	th the Port of Seattle\, bringing together local professionals\, entrepren
	eurs\, and community leaders for an evening of connection\, collaboration\
	, and valuable business resources. This month's mixer features a Small Bus
	iness Resource Fair\, where attendees can meet representatives from organi
	zations offering tools\, programs\, and guidance to help small businesses 
	grow and thrive. Whether you're looking to expand your network\, explore p
	artnership opportunities\, or learn about business support services\, this
	 event provides a welcoming environment to make meaningful connections. En
	joy light refreshments\, engage with fellow professionals\, and discover n
	ew resources to support your business journey-all while taking in insights
	 from the Port of Seattle about upcoming initiatives that impact our regio
	nal economy. Perfect for: ✔ Small business owners ✔ Startups and entrepren
	eurs ✔ Professionals looking to network ✔ Anyone interested in local busin
	ess resources and Port of Seattle programs We look forward to seeing you t
	here!  BUSINESS INVOLVEMENT OPPORTUNITIES: Sponsorship opportunities are s
	till available\, for more information please download our Seattle Southsid
	e Chamber Event Sponsorship Form.\n\nhttps://seatoday.6amcity.com/events/#
